field.value:
http://forum.castleproject.org/viewtopic.php?t=160
it's not  possible to map a unique key on multiple columns in Activerecord
Like we do in "standard" hibernate mapping when using the "unique-key" attribute

Something like
[Property(Unique=true,Insert=false,unique-key="AK1")]
public string Field1
{
private set {field1 = value;}
get {return field1;}
}
[Property(Unique=true,Insert=false,unique-key="AK1")]
public string Field2
{
private set{field2 = value;}
get{return field2;}
}
